<p>
  {% unless true and false and false or true %}
    <p>condition is false excute: test unless equal if not true and (false and (false or true))</p>
  {% endunless %}
</p>

<h2>9. Types 类型</h2>
<p>blank: 可用于判断字符串是否为空</p>
<p>nil: 未定义的值</p>
<p>empty: 定义但没有值的对象</p>
<p>
  {% unless pages.contact == empty %}
    <p>pages.contact is not empty {{ pages.contact.title }}</p>
  {% endunless %}
</p>

<h2>10. 注释</h2>
<p>
  {% if settings.featured_potions_title != blank %}
    {{ settings.featured_potions_title }}
